release_notes:
This release contains bug fixes from the previous beta (2022.8.692.1). We also
wanted to call out that we've made server side changes to significantly reduce
captcha issues for users with IPv6 enabled (no client related change but wanted
to call out the work).
 
## Notable updates
 
- Fixed failure to reconnect to WARP due to DNS stub server AddrInUse failures
 
## Known issues
- No known issues
 
For Zero Trust documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/cloudflare-one/connections/connect-devices/warp
 
For Consumer documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/warp-client/
